title: The Seafarers - Fighting Sail - A. Whipple.epub
description:
EPUB. A well illustrated account of naval warfare during the Napoleonic Wars. Some of the chapters are : The mighty ships of the line, The bittersweet life of a midshipman and Trafalgar: the final kill . striking color and b&w illustrations throughout.
There is no Bibliography, Acknowledgements, Picture Credits or Index. A lot of pictures were spread across two pages, they are not included, other pictures have been moved to the end of the chapter they were in.
Thanks to STBGD for the PDF upload.
